This paper discusses the development of a vector space model for analyzing text data using data mining and machine learning algorithms. The paper specifically focuses on the temporal aspect of evolving text corpora, which suggests that it may fall under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data structures (cs.DS).
